## Decisions made (plan-first, settled before code)
- **Slice-table divergence noted:** phase-1.md:1199-1201 still shows the
  ORIGINAL plan (slice 8 = Guardian+Teacher imports; slice 10 = profile +
  class-teacher only). Reality: slice 8 deferred teacher import (rationale
  in 2026-05-29 journal, not in phase-1.md), slice 10 absorbs it. The spec
  table is stale; don't trust it for slice scope.
- **Q1 — TeacherProfile schema:** ship the pinned shape verbatim
  (phase-1.md:366-383). Includes `nutNumber`; omits `notes`.
- **joinedAt vs hireDate:** keep spec's `joinedAt DateTime @default(now())`.
  Real admin-entered hire date is Phase 3 payroll territory.
- **Q2 — profile lifecycle = Option A (admin-explicit, CSV invite-only).**
  Profile created only via POST /teacher-profiles after accept, real
  admin-entered staffNumber. NO auto-create on accept (teacher portal
  shows empty-state). Teacher CSV = email+firstName+lastName only;
  importing staffNumber/specialty is DEFERRED to a future slice (capture
  in deferred.md). Zero schema deviation; passes acceptance #7;
  deliverable-18 read as "can get a profile," not "auto-gets one."
- **Q3 — class-teacher assignment: already shipped in slice 3.** FK on
  ClassArm → users.id, persistent, multiple arms per teacher, onDelete
  SetNull + soft-delete handling. assertUserIsTeacher + create/PATCH +
  the settings/class-arms dropdown UI all exist. Slice 10 only CONSUMES
  it (staff UI); no new assignment mechanism.
- **Blocker — no `teacher` system role is seeded** (only owner+admin;
  full rollup deferred to slice 13). Without it invite-accept of a
  teacher rolls back and assertUserIsTeacher always fails. **Decision:
  pull a MINIMAL teacher role seed forward into slice 10 cp1** (role row +
  read-scoped perms per phase-1.md:1087); full rollup + existing-school
  migration stays slice 13.
- **Q4 — teacher CSV: confirmed routine.** Third branch in the existing
  imports.processor dispatcher (not a new @Processor). validate-teachers
  .engine.ts + commit-teachers.row.ts (Invitation-creating per row).
  teacherImportRowSchema in packages/types/src/imports/. Route =
  /staff/import (4th wizard-ui.tsx consumer). ImportJobType.TEACHERS enum
  already exists. One `teacher.import.commit` audit per job.
- **SD count stays 4.** All endpoints post-tenant.
- **Acceptance bar:** slice 10 LAYS GROUNDWORK, does not close
  deliverable-18. It ships profile + class-teacher; TeacherAssignment +
  teacher portal + scope filter (acceptance #9) are slice 11.

